reviewText: Michael Cavanaugh is a great guy and certainly a talented musician. I met him following a show of his and he was a class act. Glad to support him.
High energy album with nearly non-stop music of Billy Joel and others.  Michael Cavanaugh is quite a musician and overall performer.

I saw Mr. Cavanaugh in concert and I loved the show so much I purchased the DVD. Damn good concert. Great video and sound.

If you like Billy Joel you will love Michael! One hell of a talented person.

We were actually at this show in Riverside 4th row.  The show itself was amazing and both my husband and I were really glad it was recorded.  We watched the DVD last night and the production quality is superb, the sound is excellent & Michael is amazing.  Wonderful show and even better DVD.  I highly recomend this DVD to anyone who is a fan of Billy Joel, you won't be disappointed!!
